00:00:41,966 --> 00:00:44,100
<c.Japanese>（元子）<c.Japanese>澄江</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>すみえ</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>が私のために<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

