（<c.Japanese>麻理</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>まり</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>）ママ 私たちは？</c.Japanese>

164
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,033
<c.Japanese>（元子）みんな<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

165
00:11:05,933 --> 00:11:08,133
<c.Japanese>“ロダン”という
